{"tid":1335610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721行程集中討論] 西環(法輪功遊行) 或 銅鑼環(多商場)","createTime":"2019-07-20T14:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:41:51.000Z","uid":199739,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4203e343009658087d1a549b4dcecdc7dec593b4","tid":1335610,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"唔係話想做網絡軍師<br />\n但而家民陣遊行要係修頓停 一定好擠逼<br />\n<br />\n網上好多唔同意見 加上灣仔難走<br />\n我認為聽日情況會好亂<br />\n希望今晚大家可以有定個共識<br />\n當然到時都可以睇現場情況決定<br />\n<br />\n想大家係度講返你支持嘅方案<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">再講下原因同討論下建議嘅路線</span><br />\n<br />\n[立場] 灣仔是個凶險之地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335299</a><br />\n<br />\n法輪功周日下午大遊行（北角去西環） 已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335146</a><br />\n<br />\n[公投] 721 終點係金鐘定老銅?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324076</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />西環<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />銅鑼環"},{"pid":"0c126893b48a3fadad5492dfc68b944cf826e9f1","tid":1335610,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"要諗點由灣仔去西環 地鐵真係承受到？ 又真係會多市民跟呢個咁迂迴嘅行程？"},{"pid":"4baaf3ec9b3430d4b34399f3401d95522085bce6","tid":1335610,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保障同行手足<br />\n向偽警說不！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【7.21有人冒警】和理非對偽警說不！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335553</a>"},{"pid":"4fbef5be6469d165872139c716416e133c3abd0b","tid":1335610,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"